snippet.title: Grand Emprise: Time Travel Survival - Official Space Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Grand Emprise: Time Travel Survival's latest trailer showcases new locations like space, mechs, gameplay, and more. Wishlist the game here, if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2236300/Grand_Emprise_Time_Travel_Survival/

Watch the trailer for another look at this upcoming survival, crafting, and base-building open-world adventure game. Grand Emprise: Time Travel Survival is coming to PC in August 2023. A playable free prologue is available on Steam on June 7, 2023.

#GameTrailers
